Assignment 01 :
---------------
Write a program to implement an interface Payable with method pay() using amount to pay.

Two classes Employee and Contractor implement it using anonymous inner class.




package Elc;
interface Payable{
	void pay(double amount);	
}



public class Employee {
public static void main(String[] args) {
		Payable employee = new Payable() {
			public void pay(double amount) {
				System.out.println("Hello i am an employee paying "+ amount);
			}	
		};
		
		Payable contractor = new Payable() {
			public void pay(double amount) {
				System.out.println("Hello i am a contractor paying "+ amount);
			}
		};
		
		employee.pay(200);
		contractor.pay(200);	
				
}
}
